FBIS3-38839 "drweu026aa_94021" FBIS-WEU-94-026 Document Type:Daily Report 8 February 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Swiss Foreign Minister Cotti Comments on Attack LD0602111194 Bern Swiss Radio International in English 0900 GMT 6 Feb 94 LD0602111194 Bern Swiss Radio International Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Swiss Foreign Minister Flavio Cotti has expressed shock at the attack in Sarajevo, stressing that the atrocity occurred just a few hundred kilometers from Switzerland. Mr. Cotti said the only way to end the bloodshed in Bosnia was by continuing peace negotiations. He also reaffirmed Switzerland's pledge of humanitarian action in the crisis.
